1世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9776c4af53a9cf71a884d38d051b4ab64f18525d","tid":1541100,"uid":310221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fda340537dceba5d25ac2072b02dbcfa76c2bbcc","tid":1541100,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"use english let others know the truth"},{"pid":"ae88b123f3ca3350754d90c581c1d2979386ce48","tid":1541100,"uid":310221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"Liberate Hong Kong! Revolution of our times!"}]}